name: Do Androids Dream of Electric Art? (No. 3)
description: An array of art critics were simulated using an AI trained on a vast corpus of human text and asked: “What are your thoughts on the Campbell’s Soup Cans paintings by Andy Warhol?” Their responses were recorded and assembled. Hover over the piece to highlight each individual response. In the spirit of Warhol’s mass produced art, this piece is offered as part of HENthousand (10k editions offered at 1 tez).
